data.description:
This lovely 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence offers a spacious and open floor plan, perfect for both comfortable living and entertaining. This home offers a newer roof (2022), bay windows, 42 inch kitchen cabinets, recess lighting, stainless steel appliances, new water heater. 
The kitchen has ample counter space, and a convenient island to help stay connected with loved ones in the adjoining living and dining area. The primary bedroom features an en-suite bath and a generously sized walk-in closet. The two additional bedrooms are perfect for family members, guests, or home office space. This home has a large backyard with no neighbors directly in back of the house.  You'll be delighted to discover this home is conveniently located just around the corner from the community pool. This is a perfect way to cool off on hot summer days and meet your neighbors within this friendly and welcoming community. Don't miss your opportunity to make this delightful 2005-built residence your new home.
